val <- map_dfr(util_years(), ~utilization(year = .x, city = "Valdosta", state = "GA", type = "provider")) |> 
  select(year, entity_type, gender, credential, specialty, par:conditions)

val |> 
  mutate(coin_deduct = tot_allowed - tot_payment, .after = tot_payment) |> 
  mutate(srvcs_per_bene = tot_srvcs / tot_benes, .after = tot_srvcs) |> 
  mutate(pay_per_srvc = tot_payment / tot_srvcs, .after = tot_srvcs) |> 
  select(-c(par, demographics, conditions)) |> 
  gt_preview(top_n = 10, bottom_n = 10) |> 
  opt_table_font(font = google_font(name = "Fira Code")) |> 
  opt_stylize() |> 
  opt_all_caps()

val |> 
  group_by(year) |> 
  summarise(
    provs = n(),
    benes = sum(tot_benes),
    srvcs = sum(tot_srvcs), 
    pymt = sum(tot_payment),
    .groups = "drop") |> 
  change(!year) |> 
  select(year,
         provs,
         provs_chg,
         provs_pct,
         provs_ror = provs_pct_ror,
         benes,
         benes_chg,
         benes_pct,
         benes_ror = benes_pct_ror,
         srvcs,
         srvcs_chg,
         srvcs_pct,
         srvcs_ror = srvcs_pct_ror,
         pymt,
         pymt_chg,
         pymt_pct,
         pymt_ror = pymt_pct_ror,) |> 
  gt(rowname_col = "year") |> 
  sub_zero(zero_text = "") |> 
  sub_missing(missing_text = "") |>
  fmt_integer(columns = c(provs, benes, srvcs, pymt), sep_mark = ",", suffixing = TRUE) |>
  fmt_integer(columns = ends_with("chg"), force_sign = TRUE, sep_mark = ",", suffixing = TRUE) |>
  fmt_percent(columns = ends_with("pct"), force_sign = TRUE, decimals = 1) |>
  fmt_percent(columns = ends_with("ror"), decimals = 1) |>
  cols_label(
    provs = "Tot",

    provs_ror = "RoR",
    provs_pct = "%",
    benes = "Tot",
    benes_chg = "Abs",
    benes_ror = "RoR",
    benes_pct = "%",
    srvcs = "Tot",
    srvcs_chg = "Abs",
    srvcs_ror = "RoR",
    srvcs_pct = "%",
    pymt = "Tot",

  cols_hide(columns = c(benes, srvcs, pymt)) |> 
  tab_spanner(label = "Providers",
    columns = c(provs, provs_chg, provs_ror, provs_pct)) |> 
  tab_spanner(label = "Payment",
    columns = c(pymt, pymt_chg, pymt_ror, pymt_pct)) |>
  tab_spanner(label = "Beneficiaries",

  opt_stylize(color = "red")

srvc |> 
  dplyr::group_by(year, family) |> 
  dplyr::mutate(hcpcs_level = dplyr::min_rank(dplyr::pick(avg_allowed, avg_payment))) |>

  gt_preview(top_n = 30) |>
